{"tid":1648353,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"成撚日話要衝出國際, 但最多遊客既尖沙咀唔行","createTime":"2019-10-12T07:16:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T05:44:06.000Z","uid":23451,"like":67,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"38729e42bd34f95f2858741bb9a2799afb6bcfe2","tid":1648353,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T07:16:23.000Z","msg":"之前出過好幾次post<br />\n我係某名店sales，已辭工<br />\n廣東道海防道彌敦道呢三條圍住既正方形區係最多遊客<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oo6tgGA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Foo6tgGA.jpg&h=7f64814d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n講過好多次<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但次次都係就咁極速路過</span></span><br />\n佢地連店都唔關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />毫無影響<br />\n行去深水埗係有咩意義？<br />\n<br />\n成日話要衝出國際<br />\n點解唔趁行緊尖沙咀果陣直接派文宣俾旅客？<br />\n第一身派點都有效過你網上宣傳<br />\n尤其俾人知我地唔係暴徒<br />\n<br />\n政府係勁怕外資壓力<br />\n呢排已經係咁報零售業跌幅<br />\n好多公司高層開始癲"},{"pid":"86961ba96d0b4ec2d0da523240ac20e027dc9865","tid":1648353,"uid":23451,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T07:17:28.000Z","msg":"公司每個月做緊2,3千萬生意<br />\n呢幾個月跌左800-1000萬"},{"pid":"c436965d69830c3bba4f036a7f211a35edc2d706","tid":1648353,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T07:17:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea067c6843e5f88a8d560d332b27b9440f03ecc2","tid":1648353,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T07:19:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e4f1f15540b6e4cd18e8d02159cc4b4d6ba0e6f","tid":1648353,"uid":23451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T07:19:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb2c1cf50fe22fe8ac919371add5ec716f83746b","tid":1648353,"uid":129537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite